 50 year old man arrested The police in Lagos state has arrested Taiwo Oyelabi, 50, living in Community Road, Badore, Iba, for sexually abusing and impregnating his daughter, aged 21. The suspect who works as security guard, is currently in the police custody while his pregnant daughter has been taken to the hospital for proper medical attention. When interrogated, Taiwo who spoke in pidgin said  ”I gave birth to her. I am the one that got her pregnant”.   comments  The post 50 year old man arrested for impregnating his 21 year old daughter in Lagos (photos) appeared first on INFORMATION NIGERIA. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from INFORMATION NIGERIA. Click here to read the full text on the original website.